*** add this dependency   -------  debugImplementation "androidx.fragment:fragment-testing:1.3.0-alpha08"
*** then goto project view
***inside src folder create a debug name folder and create other package  just like com.github.androiddev.roomdatabase_testing
***inside this package we create a class name hilttestactivity and make it as entry point  ------
@AndroidEntryPoint
class HiltTestActivity : AppCompatActivity()

***now copy our manifest file and peste it inside our debug folder and edit like this -------
---------
<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<manifest xmlns:android="http://schemas.android.com/apk/res/android"
    package="com.github.androiddeveloper3005.roomdatabase_testing" >

    <application>
        <activity
            android:name=".HiltTestActivity"
            android:exported="false" />
    </application>

</manifest>
-------

***now goto the android view of our android studio
***goto the android test folder and create a kotlin file not class------ named hiltextension
***now inside those file create a inline function and make it generic
